(25,	1420,	'RB',	'rnbanez101@gmail.com',	'',	'180.190.43.142',	'2017-09-12 21:18:52',	'2017-09-12 21:18:52',	'Realistic thought/information.',	0,	'1',	'',	'',	0,	0),
(26,	1420,	'J. O.',	'randomemail@email.com',	'',	'180.190.115.236',	'2017-09-12 21:56:01',	'2017-09-12 21:56:01',	'I know that I was not one of your best student Sir, failing my OPESYS back in 2014, but I wish you could have stayed, I have wasted so much time prioritizing unimportant things in my life. Now that the time has come that I want to take the COMSEC track under your tutelage, you are now gone, thank you for being my Professor in two of subjects. I hope life fairs well for you Sir. the last time I spoke to you was in a symposium speaker about social jackers - J. O. / J. C.',	0,	'1',	'',	'',	0,	0),
(27,	1420,	'Deeno Lapira',	'deenolapira@gmail.com',	'',	'202.57.42.226',	'2017-09-13 00:39:12',	'2017-09-13 00:39:12',	'Thank you, Sir Justin for this wonderful sharing of your learning experiences.  As I was reading through it, I had some flashbacks in my mind...these will serve as an inspiration to be better each time I face a new class,  be more compassionate and understanding of my students. I wish you well in all your undertakings and hope that we can have you back in the academe soon!  All the best and God bless you!',	0,	'1',	'',	'',	0,	0),
(28,	1477,	'John Doe',	'johndoe@email.com',	'',	'112.206.137.189',	'2019-03-31 10:19:18',	'2019-03-31 10:19:18',	'This is great. Last February 24, 2017, me and my undergraduate students went to the University of Asia and the Pacific (UA&amp;P) in Pasig City to present their project Hydra in a school-initiated research.',	0,	'0',	'Mozilla/5.0 (Linux; Android 8.0.0; LDN-LX2) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/73.0.3683.90 Mobile Safari/537.36',	'',	0,	0);
